{"tid":134080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警自比二戰猶太人 消息：違反紀律行為準則","createTime":"2017-02-25T07:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T18:13:27.000Z","uid":5195,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4f9add4bd09ed4a508950863404860a255dfdb","tid":134080,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:49:30.000Z","msg":"有警員於周三晚的撐七警大會上，將香港警察比作二戰時期的猶太人，稱猶如被納粹德軍迫害，以色列及德國兩個駐港領事館先後指言。《南華早報》今日引述警方消息指，警隊高層擬約以色列及德國兩個駐港領事館會面，希望解釋清楚情況及澄清任何誤會。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，警隊高層認為，需向兩領事館強調有關言論不代表警方立場，有需要在情況惡化前向兩領事館澄清。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指警方高層形容事件已失控，擔心令警方在國際上的形象受損，擔心兩領事館正式向特區政府投訴，屆時成外交事件，屆時警方將難以處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n南華引述消息指出，涉事警員違反警隊的紀律及行為的準則。"},{"pid":"af04e0e32cb14d4be19ea235dab5bb81297f89aa","tid":134080,"uid":1799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/155341_df51966e50894bde8df32bf1b5d8f2aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F155341_df51966e50894bde8df32bf1b5d8f2aa.jpg&h=8e784e64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e1090de24b27e0e1bb62c94d73be6bcc4804508","tid":134080,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfeddff62d3431ce01d615f738fbc0629cb2c1d","tid":134080,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"becef0d322607d72eb0902fd57bb81e11c1d9f6b","tid":134080,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"h